dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Alan Davis. May I please have your name?
Hi there, my name is Shirley Adams.
Nice to meet you, Shirley. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's three two six four five.
Thank you, Shirley. Additionally, could you confirm the make and model of your insured vehicle?
Of course, it's a two zero one eight Toyota Corolla.
Great, thank you for that information. Now, may I know your date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, it's the eleventh of August, nineteen eighty-seven.
Thank you, Shirley, for sharing that with me. I have noted the details provided. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Alan, for your help.
You're welcome, Shirley. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!
